  lightning rods.</b></p>
<p align="left"><b><a href="apr05.htm">APRIL 2005 :</a> Radio silence.</b></p>
<p align="left"><b><a href="mar05.htm">MARCH 2005 :</a> No bulletins from Hooting 
  Yard.</b></p>
<p align="left"><b><a href="feb05.htm">FEBRUARY 2005 :</a> Such an exciting month 
  at Hooting Yard that Mr Key had to go and lie down for two months, hence the 
  absence of any entries for March and April. Here you can read about bags in 
  the Bible, Rasputin, moths, the Electric Prunes, Muggletonians, haruspices, 
  and both Tiny Enid and Serpentine Claude.</b></p>
<p align="left"><b><a href="jan05.htm">JANUARY 2005 : </a>We enter the new year 
